'''FOTA'''（Firmware Over-the-Air）<ref name="theinquirer martin 2012">{{cite news | url=http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2154631/asus-set-february-android-upgrade-original-transformer | title=Asus is still set on February Android 4.0 upgrade for original Transformer | work=[[The_Inquirer|The Inquirer]] | date=February 23, 2012 | accessdate=March 27, 2012 | author=Martin, Chris | archive-date=2019-12-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225035908/https://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2154631/asus-set-february-android-upgrade-original-transformer | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="marketwatch 2012">{{cite news | url=http://www.marketwatch.com/story/bb-electronics-expands-its-wireless-reach-with-acquisition-of-conel-and-its-portfolio-of-cellular-routers-and-gateways-2012-03-02 | title=B&B Electronics Expands Its Wireless Reach with Acquisition of Conel and Its Portfolio of Cellular Routers and Gateways | work=[[MarketWatch|MarketWatch]] | date=March 2, 2012 | accessdate=March 27, 2012}}</ref><ref name="dataweek 2012">{{cite news | url=http://www.dataweek.co.za/news.aspx?pklnewsid=41364 | title=Cellular module adds FOTA, GSM positioning | work=Dataweek | date=March 7, 2012 | accessdate=March 27, 2012 | archive-date=2018-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629131546/http://www.dataweek.co.za/news.aspx?pklnewsid=41364 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="theunwired hess 2012">{{cite news | url=http://www.theunwired.net/?item=upgrade-samsung-to-offer-android-4-0-for-its-galaxy-s-ii-end-of-this-week-update | title=UPGRADE: Samsung to offer Android 4.0 for its Galaxy S II end of this week | work=The Unwired | date=March 9, 2012 | accessdate=March 27, 2012 | author=Hess, Arne | archive-date=2018-05-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508190549/http://www.theunwired.net/?item=upgrade-samsung-to-offer-android-4-0-for-its-galaxy-s-ii-end-of-this-week-update | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ibtimes gilbert 2012">{{cite news | url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/311768/20120309/samsung-galaxy-s2-ice-cream-sandwich.htm | title=Samsung Galaxy S2 Ice Cream Sandwich Update Confirmed (Then Retracted) | work=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]] | date=March 9, 2012 | accessdate=March 27, 2012 | author=Gilbert, David | archive-date=2013-09-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927190459/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/311768/20120309/samsung-galaxy-s2-ice-cream-sandwich.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>通常譯為'''無線韌體更新'''或'''無線韌體升級''' ，是用於[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]和[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]的升級，包括軟件更新、韌體更新和設備管理等功能。起初，[[手機|手機]]的韌體更新需要到設備廠商指定的服務中心進行，接收更新的另一種方法是將設備連入[[電腦|電腦]]進行升級。但這兩種方法的缺點是很不方便。因此，現在很多的移動設備製造商已經採納FOTA技術為設備進行更新。如果移動設備具有FOTA功能，移動設備製造商和運營商可以將新韌體透過網絡向設備“推送”更新訊息，這降低了韌體更新的成本，提高了消費者的滿意度。

